      "acceptanceCriteria": "CFD solver must have documented version control, regression testing, and release notes consistent with MRL 2 requirements.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 19.2 used for all simulations. Vendor-supplied QA documentation confirms version control and regression test suite. Release notes reviewed and archived. Achieved level meets required level for MRL 2."
